Last weekend my family threw D & I a baby shower. Thank you so much to everyone who came from near and far to celebrate this blessing in our lives. The support and love that I have experienced as this baby has been growing is something I can’t really put into words. What I can say is I’m grateful, honored and truly in awe of everything I’ve experienced the last 9 months. Now we wait for baby’s birthday 🥲🥹🧡
First birthday in my mom era 🧡 so grateful for all the love I have been blessed with this year & all that is to come in the next ✨ thanks for all the wishes, it means so much.
Finally shook the newborn dust off and stepped out 🫠 so proud of you @michelle_arcane & @arcanecollaboratory @archivesantostudio

This year was full of so much change, so many blessings and an abundance of love. Thankful to go into the new year as a family of 3 surrounded by love and so much adventure on the horizon. Happy new year 🧡 #2024
